   --

   This plugin generates draw.io diagrams that may reference SAP BTP service
   icons and shapes provided by the SAP `btp-solution-diagrams` repository
   (https://github.com/SAP/btp-solution-diagrams), which is also licensed
   under Apache-2.0. SAP shape libraries are NOT bundled with this plugin —
   the plugin downloads them from the official SAP GitHub repository at
   first invocation. Users are responsible for complying with SAP's
   licensing terms when distributing diagrams generated with this plugin.

